#: ../source/reference/method/db.collection.validate.txt:18
msgid ""
"Validates a collection. The method scans a collection's data structures "
"for correctness and returns a single :term:`document` that describes the "
"relationship between the logical collection and the physical "
"representation of the data."
msgstr ""

